returns._0: total The total amount to be repaid

params.leaseId: The ID of the lease to fulfill

params.moduleTypeId: The ID of the module type to check

returns._0: True if this module matches the given type, false otherwise

params.smartAccount: The smart account to transfer tokens from
params.to: The lease creator address who will receive the tokens
params.token: The token address (address(0) for native token)

calculateRepaymentAmount(address,uint256.notice: Calculates the total repayment amount including interest

checkLeaseExpiry(address,uint256).notice: Checks and updates the lease status if it has expired.

fulfillLease(address,uint256).notice: Fulfills a specific lease with interest

isInitialized(address).notice: Checks if the module is initialized on a smart account.

isModuleType(uint256).notice: Checks if this module matches the given module type ID

name().notice: Returns the name of the module.

onInstall(bytes).notice: Called when the module is installed on a smart account.

onUninstall(bytes).notice: Called when the module is uninstalled from a smart account.

startLease(address,address,uint256,addre.notice: Starts a new lease for the specified token and amount

updateLeaseConfig(address,(address,uint2.notice: Updates the lease configuration for a specific token.

version().notice: Returns the version of the module.
